description: Details of Code for Sustainable Homes (interim assessment), pursuant to condition 8 of planning permission P/2013/1576 dated 05/07/2013 for Internal and external alterations in conjunction with the conversion of the proposed gymnasium and cycle store on ground floor fronting Singapore Road to eight one bedroom flats (2 wheelchair accessible, the other 6 with rear courtyards), revised cycle storage and provision of two storey, internal access route and 11 car parking spaces (including 2 wheelchair accessible spaces).
